---
import "../../../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>LaunchTrack Privacy Policy</title>
</head>

<body>
<main class="container">

<section class="legal-page">

<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p class="last-updated">
  Last updated: December 1, 2025
</p>

<p>
  Thank you for using LaunchTrack. Your privacy is important.
  This Privacy Policy explains how the app handles your data.
</p>

<p>
  LaunchTrack is operated by Ernesto Cisnero ("we", "us", or "our").
</p>


<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

<p>
  LaunchTrack is designed to provide information about upcoming space
  launches. The app is intentionally minimal and does not collect or
  store personal data from users.
</p>

<p>
  We do not collect:
</p>

<ul>
  <li>Names</li>
  <li>Email addresses</li>
  <li>Phone numbers</li>
  <li>Location data</li>
  <li>Photos, videos, or media</li>
  <li>Device identifiers</li>
  <li>Analytics or tracking information</li>
</ul>

<p>
  The only data processed is limited to what is needed to retrieve
  launch information from public APIs.
</p>


<h2>2. Data from External APIs</h2>

<p>
  LaunchTrack retrieves upcoming launch data from a third-party public API.
  This retrieval is read-only and does not involve any personal information.
</p>

<p>
  We do not control or manage the information provided by external APIs.
  No personally identifiable information (PII) is received, stored,
  or transmitted.
</p>


<h2>3. How We Use Information</h2>

<p>
  Because LaunchTrack does not collect personal data, we do not use
  personal information for any purpose.
</p>

<p>The app only performs the following actions:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Requests launch data from a public API</li>
  <li>Displays launch schedules and countdowns</li>
</ul>

<p>
  No data is used for marketing, tracking, analytics, or user profiling.
  LaunchTrack does not collect personal information from users.
  Any advertisements displayed in the app are non-personalized.
</p>


<h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>

<p>
  LaunchTrack does not use:
</p>

<ul>
  <li>Advertising services</li>
  <li>Analytics SDKs</li>
  <li>Tracking libraries</li>
  <li>Cookies</li>
  <li>Social media integrations</li>
</ul>

<p>
  The external launch API may have its own privacy policy.
  You can review their information here:
</p>

<a href="https://thespacedevs.com/" target="_blank">
  TheSpaceDevs
</a>


<h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>

<p>
  LaunchTrack does not collect personal information and is safe for users
  of all ages. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children
  under 13.
</p>


<h2>6. Security</h2>

<p>
  Since LaunchTrack does not store or transmit personal data,
  no personal data can be exposed or compromised.
</p>

<p>
  Network requests to external APIs use secure HTTPS whenever available.
</p>


<h2>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>
  We may update this Privacy Policy if features change.
  Any updates will be posted on this page with a new "Last updated" date.
</p>


<h2>8. Contact Us</h2>

<p>
  If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us:
</p>

<a href="/">
  Ernesto Cisnero
</a>

</section>

</main>
</body>
</html>